(16, '2015-09-18 01:09:33', 'PROCUREMENT\r\nASSISTANCE', 1, 1, '/image/history1.jpg', '/image/history2.jpg', '', 0, '<p>MEDPARK was founded in 2012, headquartered in Amstelveen, the Netherlands. We adopt a global approach spanning professional disciplines, industry sectors and national borders. Our company is an official distributor of leading manufacturers of diagnostic and therapeutic medical equipment.</p>', '\n  <div id="info">\n      <div class="full-width-container">\n          <div class="container">\n              <div class="row">\n                  <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 bg-1 fw col-sm-8">\n                     <div class="block-1 left-side oneHeight" style="height: 550px;">\n                          <div class="wow fadeInLeft animated" data-wow-delay="0.3s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.3s; animation-name: fadeInLeft;">\n                             <div class="thumb-pad-1">\n                                 <div class="thumbnail">\n                                     <div class="caption">\n                                      <h1 class="black_title">Spectrum<br><span>can assist you in</span></h1>\n                                        <ul class="listed">\n                                           <li>Preparation of detailed specifications and data sheets for various plants, equipment, machinery and system</li>\n                                           <li>Invite bids for supply of various plant equipment, machinery and systems</li>\n                                           <li>Prepare detailed tender documents for supply and installation of various systems like HVAC, Water treatment and distribution, Electrical, Steam generation and distribution etc.</li>\n                                           <li>Techno-commercial evaluation of the bids and recommend the best alternative</li>\n                                           <li>Checking & approval of vendor drawings</li>\n                                           <li>Checking & approval of contractors site erection drawings</li>\n                                           <li>Preparation of Factory Acceptance Test protocols</li>\n                                           <li>Expediting with vendors for timely supply of all machinery and equipment</li>\n                                           <li>Expediting with vendors for timely supply of all machinery and equipment</li>\n                                         </ul> \n                                     </div>\n                                 </div>\n                             </div>\n                         </div>\n                     </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4">\n                      <div class="block-1 bg-2 fw right-side oneHeight" style="height: 550px;">     \n                          <div class="wow fadeInRight animated" data-wow-delay="0.3s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.3s; animation-name: fadeInRight;">\n                              <div class="box-1">\n                                  <h1 class="red_title">PROCUREMENT<br>ASSISTANCE</h1>\n                                  <p>Spectrum with more than 16 years of experience can suggest the best equipment, machinery and system with the right blend of economy and quality.</p>\n                              </div>\n                          </div>\n                      </div> \n                  </div>\n\n\n\n\n              </div>\n          </div> \n      </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n'),
(17, '2015-09-18 01:09:33', 'PROJECT MANAGEMENT', 1, 1, '/image/history1.jpg', '/image/history2.jpg', '', 0, '<p>MEDPARK was founded in 2012, headquartered in Amstelveen, the Netherlands. We adopt a global approach spanning professional disciplines, industry sectors and national borders. Our company is an official distributor of leading manufacturers of diagnostic and therapeutic medical equipment.</p>', ' <div id="info">\n      <div class="full-width-container">\n          <div class="container">\n              <div class="row">\n                  <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 bg-1 fw col-sm-8">\n                     <div class="block-1 left-side oneHeight" style="height: 600px;">\n                          <div class="wow fadeInLeft animated" data-wow-delay="0.3s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.3s; animation-name: fadeInLeft;">\n                             <div class="thumb-pad-1">\n                                 <div class="thumbnail">\n                                     <div class="caption">\n                                      <h1 class="black_title">The Project management <br>\n                                      <span>functions would include:</span></h1>\n                                        \n                                        <ul class="listed">\n                                          <li>Developing mutually agreed co-ordination procedure defining formal line of communication between Client and Consultant</li>\n                                          <li>Prepare project schedule to monitor progress of Engineering, Procurement and Construction activities</li>\n                                          <li>Update schedule of work / bar chart based on the progress of work</li>\n                                          <li>Conduct periodic co-ordination meetings with Client to review actual progress of work as against planned work schedule and remove bottlenecks</li>\n                                          <li>Propose c