(1, 'About Us', '/', '<div class="container descr_cat">\n<p>Healthcare systems around the world are facing unprecedented change. While healthcare is primarily organized within national geographies, the issues are truly global. <br /><br />Demographics, financial restraint, new technologies and consumer expectations are creating significant challenges and opportunities. <br /><br />In these unpredictable times, healthcare leaders require insight and guidance from an adviser and a supplier you can trust. That is why leading organizations turn to MEDPARK. We are willing to take on the challenges that industry gives us and find the most complicated and effective solutions to solve your problems.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="row img3">\n<img src="/image/about_us_big.jpg">\n</div>\n', ''),
(2, 'Products & Solutions', '/', '<div class="container descr_cat"> <span>MEDPARK brings value-added solutions to healthcare business development and capital equipment financing.</span> <p>At the heart of our philosophy is one important commitment: you’ll have a single point of contact throughout your project’s lifecycle. Our team offers unparalleled expertise in every aspect of developing, diagnostic imaging and radiation therapy service lines, including business modeling, selection and optimization of equipment, facility design, construction supervision, licensing and credentialing, as well as comprehensive marketing solutions. They’ll be at your side throughout every step of the process to ensure successful completion and implementation of your project.</p> </div> \n\n\n<div class="row img1"><img src="/image/products_solutions_2.jpg"> </div> \n\n<div class="container descr_cat"> <span>The MEDPARK project oversight team has the knowledge and expertise related specifically to healthcare facility renovation and construction to:</span> <p><li> Conduct pre-construction analysis.</li> <li> Recommend accessible, consumer focused designs.</li> <li> Coordinate plan design and review processes.</li> <li> Establish open lines of communication.</li> <li> Implement conflict resolution processes.</li> <li> Expedite permit and inspection processes.</li> <li> Maintain chronological project records and inspection reports.</li> <li> Assist with contractor and subcontractor selection</li> <li> Coordinate utility and infrastructure needs</li> <li> Monitor construction and quality</li> <li> Monitor cost and rate of completion</li> <li> Ensure adherence to regulations and codes</li> <li> Coordinate utility shutdowns</li></p> <br /><br /> <span>As part of MEDPARK`s turnkey solution for radiotherapy and diagnostic imaging centers, we provide insight about and assistance for:</span><br /> <p><li> Tailoring capital equipment purchases to specific business forecasts.</li> <li> Facilitating equipment testing and inspection.</li> <li> Maximizing security and minimizing risk in the physical environment</li> <li> Analyzing patient volumes and referral patterns.</li> <li> Identifying competitive pricing options for providers.</li> <li> Acquiring medical and office equipment</li> <li> Providing standing operating procedures</li> <li> Expedite equipment purchase, delivery, set-up and testing.</li></p> </div> <div class="row img2"><img src="/image/products_solutions_1.jpg"> </div> <div class="container descr_cat"> <span>Our solutions focus on enhancing revenue opportunities, improving competitive service line positioning, and delivering cutting-edge patient care. Supported equipment includes:</span> <p><li> CT scan systems.</li> <li> PET/CT scanners.</li> <li> Cyclotrons</li> <li> Mobile PET units.</li> <li> Radiotherapy modalities.</li> <li> Nuclear Medicine.</li> <li> Digital X-ray systems.</li> <li> MRI systems.</li> <li> C-Arms.</li> <li> Ultrasound.</li> <li> Digital Mammography</li> <li> Radiographic Rooms: CR/DR</li></p> </div><br /><br />\n\n\n', ''),
